{"tid":1510646,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"累己累人 - 邁克","createTime":"2019-08-27T09:11:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T09:17:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a55a7b692050d3d36b9fb9b1f642bb199485bd74","tid":1510646,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:11:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%82%81%E5%85%8B/daily/article/20190827/20756355\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2582%2581%25E5%2585%258B%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190827%2F20756355&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi7BzIjlmttHRdZ2xAWa028c%3D&h=0c5680e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2582%2581%25E5%2585%258B%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190827%2F20756355&h=72c7aaa5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%82%81%E5%85%8B/daily/article/20190827/20756355</a><br />\n<br />\n累己累人 - 邁克<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190827/large/1566806509_3c7c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190827%2Flarge%2F1566806509_3c7c.jpg&h=1fd0854a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n八二五香港警察終於向市民開槍，你話我危言聳聽都要講，讓子彈飛的時代不幸已經降臨，離六四式屠城還遠嗎？難為前一天怠工教主林鄭竟然大言不慚「大家都累了」，早就被全世界disconnect的她，憑什麼貿貿然跑出來跟狂警和藤條黨爭鋒頭，人家無差別周街狩獵的時候，她不是躲在冷氣房懶畫眉嗎，幾時有資格學人嬌滴滴叫攰？我的朋友楊某在台北有位閨密，豐乳肥臀和號稱玉婆的已故荷里活女星伊莉莎白泰萊等量齊觀，還camp精附體自封伊莉莎白太累哩，以禮賓府女寨主醜死鬼的三圍，算了吧。何況真正攰到趴低的，是連續爬山兩個幾月的示威者，和站在前線守護他們的良心記者及急救員，槍林彈雨出生入死，血汗淚貨真價實，擅長哽咽的表演藝術家唔該借歪，出自詩人筆下的「侍兒扶起嬌無力」乃貴妃專利，不是還珠格格而是賤賤格格的一介狗官累什麼累，累己累人就有你份。<br />\n<br />\n老實說，天天看警方發言人借記招之名漫漫無際講大話，打開電腦盡見大街小巷暴警合法狂毆市民，誰不感到疲倦，但比起親赴戰地為自由理想抗爭的義士，簡直蚊髀同牛髀，只有不知天高地厚，才會單方面勾肩搭背疾呼「大家都累了」。這就像，每逢在陌生人面前暴露戲迷真身，宣稱由華格納歌劇至歌舞伎多多益善，總獲得「嘩，坐成四五粒鐘噃，你唔覺得辛苦咩」的垂詢，彷彿將屁股安放在沙發椅是天大的委屈，唯有冒住被指寸嘴的危險答覆：「做戲嗰個先至辛苦，如果印印腳坐響度睇戲都埋怨，會畀雷公劈㗎！」 <br />\n<br />\n邁克<br />\n電郵 :heartsociety2@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n找不到陪跑員 (李純恩)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n當警察開槍是克制 (曾志豪)"},{"pid":"a52799166d8ed35345d8be08d53cab1a07a4166a","tid":1510646,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:12:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NSAWdB2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNSAWdB2.jpg&h=7e1fa5a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cdb1e83ff9cd1101707b15525c38d8246c828dcf","tid":1510646,"uid":81982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:12:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"783546864d08671dee5ef8c4f62937b066058cf0","tid":1510646,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:12:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi7BzIjlmttHRdZ2xAWa028c%3D&h=359a8c02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi7BzIjlmttHRdZ2xAWa028c%3D&h=5c9ad9ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi7BzIjlmttHRdZ2xAWa028c%3D&h=ab9a346b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"d12098c9ade9c97369956ec9746633a1725aa32f","tid":1510646,"uid":174498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:12:41.000Z","msg":"推，必須快過呂"},{"pid":"5e525dea62